<A>__{they climb from the station wagon into cold, clear sunlight. stare in wonder at the naked rock. the snapped, spent, cables. only shards of wood and glass leaving a hapless trail toward the cliff. bunny runs toward the debris, and through it. to a tangle of bushes near the cliff. he walks to a broken cable. crouches. his eyes running over the space. where his ancestor's home once stood. and then. he turns...}
